rimary/5 group\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-left h-4 w-4 mr-2 transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-1\"><path d=\"m12 19-7-7 7-7\"></path><path d=\"M19 12H5\"></path></svg>Back to Journal</button></a><article class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-12\"><div class=\"space-y-6 text-center lg:text-left\"><span class=\"px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-primary\">Design</span><h1 class=\"text-3xl lg:text-6xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-foreground leading-tight\">Designing for Serenity</h1><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center lg:justify-start gap-8 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-foreground/40\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar h-4 w-4\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path></svg>January 28, 2026</div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-user h-4 w-4\"><path d=\"M19 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H9a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg>By <!-- -->Sumegha</div></div></div><div class=\"relative aspect-[21/9] rounded-[3rem] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border-4 border-white\"><img alt=\"Designing for Serenity\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fpicsum.photos%2Fseed%2Fblog3%2F1200%2F600&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fpicsum.photos%2Fseed%2Fblog3%2F1200%2F600&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fpicsum.photos%2Fseed%2Fblog3%2F1200%2F600&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fpicsum.photos%2Fseed%2Fblog3%2F1200%2F600&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fpicsum.photos%2Fseed%2Fblog3%2F1200%2F600&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fpicsum.photos%2Fseed%2Fblog3%2F1200%2F600&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fpicsum.photos%2Fseed%2Fblog3%2F1200%2F600&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fpicsum.photos%2Fseed%2Fblog3%2F1200%2F600&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fpicsum.photos%2Fseed%2Fblog3%2F1200%2F600&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-12 pt-8\"><div class=\"flex-grow space-y-8\"><div class=\"prose prose-pink max-w-none\"><p class=\"text-lg lg:text-xl text-foreground/70 leading-relaxed font-light whitespace-pre-line\">Your home should be your sanctuary. The art you choose plays a vital role in setting the tone of your living space. Designing for serenity isn&#x27;t about filling every corner; it&#x27;s about choosing pieces that breathe and bring peace.\n\nMinimalist art with organic textures, like our ceramic vases or subtle wall hangings, can anchor a room without overwhelming it. We believe that art should invite stillness, providing a visual resting place in a world that never stops moving.</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 pt-8\"><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-